import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import Principal from "./Componentes/Principal"
import DetailsPage from "./Componentes/DetailsPage"
import CartPage from "./Componentes/CartPage"
import  { Routes, Route, BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom';


const datos= [
  {
    id: "1",
    imagen: "url(/src/Fotos/Anteojos/ali-pazani-GwglcplmXDs-unsplash.jpg)",
    titulo: "Primavera",
    info: "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus minus eligendi minima reiciendis fugit inventore, ullam, repellat doloremque, assumenda voluptate libero accusantium itaque maiores cum?",
    talles: ["D", "M", "L"],
    colores: ["Verde", "Negro", "Blanco"],
    precio: "1500"
  },
  {
    id: "2",
    imagen: "url(/src/Fotos/Anteojos/Anteojos.jpg.webp)",
    titulo: "Fiesta",
    info: "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus minus eligendi minima reiciendis fugit inventore, ullam, repellat doloremque, assumenda voluptate libero accusantium itaque maiores cum?",
    talles: ["D", "M", "L"],
    colores: ["Azul", "Negro", "Blanco"],
    precio: "500"
  },
  {
    id: "3",
    imagen: "url(/src/Fotos/Anteojos/apostolos-vamvouras-mKi4QEJXRCs-unsplash.jpg.webp)",
    titulo: "Vacaciones",
    info: "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus minus eligendi minima reiciendis fugit inventore, ullam, repellat doloremque, assumenda voluptate libero accusantium itaque maiores cum?",
    talles: ["D", "M", "L"],
    colores: ["Rojo", "Negro", "Blanco"],
    precio: "2000"
  }
]


function App(){
  return(
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path='/' exact element={<Principal datos= {datos}/>}/>
        <Route path='/details/:id' element={<DetailsPage datos= {datos}/>}/>
        <Route path='/cart' element={<CartPage datos= {datos}/>}/>
        <Route path='*' element={<Principal datos= {datos}/>}>
          
        </Route>
      </Routes> 
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App;
